# Patch application order. Each line is "<project> <patch>" with no whitespace
# inside either field. Externals come first so dependent framework/Launcher3
# patches see the modified headers/exports.
external/google-highway patches/external-google-highway.patch
external/skia patches/external-skia.patch
external/XMP-Toolkit-SDK patches/external-XMP-Toolkit-SDK.patch
art patches/art.patch
device/google/cuttlefish patches/device-google-cuttlefish.patch
frameworks/av patches/frameworks-av.patch
# frameworks/base is patched twice on purpose: the first patch is the generic
# desktop framework changes (DesktopExperienceFlags, SettingsProvider seed, QS
# changes); the second is the native-bridge-only changes (NativeLibraryHelper,
# PackageAbiHelperImpl). They touch disjoint files, so order is not critical,
# but keep them as separate patches so the native-bridge work can be reverted
# independently when chasing an AOSP rebase.
frameworks/base patches/frameworks-base.patch
frameworks/base patches/frameworks-base-native-bridge.patch
system/core patches/system-core.patch
system/sepolicy patches/system-sepolicy.patch
packages/apps/Launcher3 patches/packages-apps-Launcher3.patch
# Supplementary show-desktop proxy patch — applies on top of the main
# Launcher3 patch and keeps the small SystemUiProxy wrapper isolated from the
# large base patch's other SystemUiProxy hunks.
packages/apps/Launcher3 patches/packages-apps-Launcher3-show-desktop-proxy.patch
# Supplementary dynamic-display patch — applies on top of the main Launcher3
# patch. Delivers R1 (IDP recompute on display resize), Fix 2a (push fresh
# DP into the all-apps grid), Fix 2d (taskbar popup anchored above the bar
# with WindowManager.currentWindowMetrics-based maxY clamping), Fix 2e (re-
# enable taskbar recreate on screen-size / orientation changes for desktop
# displays only), and Fix 2f (taskbar fullscreen window size from live
# WindowMetrics, not cached DeviceProfile). Kept separate so the dynamic-
# display logic can be reverted independently when chasing an upstream
# rebase of the main Launcher3 patch.
packages/apps/Launcher3 patches/packages-apps-Launcher3-dynamic-display.patch
# Supplementary visual-effects patch — applies on top of the main Launcher3
# patch and keeps desktop polish toggles isolated from behavior fixes.
packages/apps/Launcher3 patches/packages-apps-Launcher3-visual-effects.patch
# Supplementary taskbar-deep-shortcuts patch — applies on top of the main
# Launcher3 patch. Single-hunk fix that unstubs app deep shortcuts in the
# taskbar long-press popup (upstream TaskbarPopupController forces them to 0
# for DISPLAY_TASKBAR icons; the data path actually works).
packages/apps/Launcher3 patches/packages-apps-Launcher3-taskbar-deep-shortcuts.patch
# Supplementary live-bounds patch — applies on top of the taskbar popup/deep
# shortcut fixes and keeps runtime taskbar placement tied to WindowMetrics
# instead of stale DeviceProfile screen dimensions.
packages/apps/Launcher3 patches/packages-apps-Launcher3-live-display-bounds.patch
vendor/lineage patches/vendor-lineage.patch
build/release patches/build-release.patch
